No one is seeing us

6
00:00:15,843 --> 00:00:17,909
or the size of this catastrophe

7
00:00:17,931 --> 00:00:20,731
and the crime we are experiencing in Gaza.

8
00:00:24,147 --> 00:00:25,827
[Reporter on air crying]

9
00:00:30,098 --> 00:00:33,555
No international security at all,

10
