15
00:00:49,180 --> 00:00:50,860
they are merely slogans.

16
00:00:51,020 --> 00:00:53,064
[Taking off helmet] We are losing souls,

17
00:00:53,120 --> 00:00:54,560
one after another.

18
00:00:56,638 --> 00:00:59,932
We are victims, directly on live television.

19
00:01:00,860 --> 00:01:03,526
We are losing souls one after the other,

20
00:01:03,681 --> 00:01:05,361
with complete immunity.

21
00:01:05,362 --> 00:01:08,262
We are martyred victims in a matter of time,

22
00:01:08,278 --> 00:01:10,811
we wait our turn, one after the other.

23
00:01:11,204 --> 00:01:14,259
Our colleague, Mohammed Abu Hatab was here,

24
00:01:14,482 --> 00:01:16,122
just half an hour ago

25
00:01:16,163 --> 00:01:17,843
and now he has left us.

26
00:01:18,047 --> 00:01:20,126
Along with his wife, and son, and brother

27
00:01:20,187 --> 00:01:22,452
and many other victims from his family,

28
